data.description: GREAT OPPORTUNITY! This 3 bedroom, 1 bath home has a Main Floor Laundry. Large open 23x14 Living Room with hardwood flooring and space for Dining Area.  The basement is ready to be finished for additional future living space. Partially fenced yard with vinyl fencing and patio. Home also has a Carport and off street parking. Some updates include vinyl siding 2014, water heater 2021, roof 2009, and furnace 2012. Home also has Central Air.
